">https://lih.kg/1659090</a>"},{"pid":"d0f7ad9c10d7fcf428beb1c0be6dfe831e038478","tid":1659704,"uid":2230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4715518ba1e2cec4e1e0634e9b034276f6831629","tid":1659704,"uid":178440,"like":70,"dislike":0,"score":70,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T05:58:36.000Z","msg":"如果有打折比黑警會唔會係集體貪污<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:13:49.000Z","msg":"洗番大陸牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4413fa11ad2beac21c799c602989983b87fe4e1a","tid":1659704,"uid":102535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:13:51.000Z","msg":"共享大灣區榮譽<br />\n生生世世留係中國啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唯有預設不推文回覆<br />\n同更改熱門準則<br />\n先可以光復連登</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<code>幫手推到連仔睇到</code><br />\n<code>幫手推到連仔睇到</code><br />\n<code>幫手推到連仔睇到</code><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">建議所有回覆預設係不推文回覆<br />\n以及修改熱門準則</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1658904\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1658904</a><br />\n<br />\n <blockquote>熱門準則<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">&bull; 單一用戶 (Unique User) 的觀看次數及停留時間。</span><br />\n&bull; 主題的發表時間：例如在「即時熱門」中，愈新發表的主題將會更容易獲得熱門分數。<br />\n&bull; 不推文回覆數量：例如在一個主題中如有大量會員使用不推文回覆，將會大幅減低熱門分數。</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">建議停留時間更改為留言次數(推文回覆)<br />\n單一用戶只計一次</span></span><br />\n相信大部分文宣或者行動Post<br />\n大家推嘅方法都係Click入去 幫手推一下<br />\n而去得到1001嘅討論Post<br />\n一定係有啲活躍User重複留言<br />\n咁樣可以提高有用Post上熱門嘅機會之餘<br />\n更可以拉得到所謂唔重要嘅Post落嚟</blockquote>"},{"pid":"63cd692238233260d20487aacabd7a5ee198b0f0","tid":1659704,"uid":175002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:14:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d082e0102b245b0ad